
1  

Kosodi kanen akaulo kaŋun, kiŋit Daudi EJAKAIT ebe, “Abwosi eoŋ mama ejai ediopet koreria luka Yuda?” Kotema EJAKAIT ŋes atiar, “Kobwot.” Kotema Daudi atiar, “Abwosi bo ai?” Kotema atiar, “Keburon.” 
2  Kwaŋin kobwot Daudi, ka akeŋor aarei da, Akinoam Ayesereelit, ka Abigail aberu kolo naka Nabal, Akaramelit. 
3  

Kitwobot Daudi ituŋa luajaas kaŋes, ŋinituŋanan ka ekaleke: kiboikinos oreria luka Keburon. 
4  

Kopotu ituŋa luka Yuda, kinyonyoikis Daudi akinyet araun ekabaka loka ekek loka Yuda kanen.

Kolimokis Daudi ebe, “Ituŋa luka Yabes-gilead kes luanukete Saul.” 
5  

Kijuka Daudi ikiyakia mama ejaas ituŋa luka Yabes-gilead, kobala kes ebe, “Kisirereŋit yes EJAKAIT, naarai itodikis ejakaitikus, ŋes Saul, asianut na, inukata ŋes. 
6  

Kitodik kwana EJAKAIT yes asianut ka abeit: eoŋ da aropi yes asianut ŋin, naarai iswamata akirot ŋin. 
7  Aso do kogogoŋoto akaninikus, kotitiŋioto: naarai atwana Saul ekusijakait, bobo da abu ekek loka Yuda kenyonyoik eoŋ akinyet araun ekabakakec.”


8  

Abu Abiner okoku loka Ner ekapolon loka ajore naka Saul koyaŋa Isboset okoku loka Saul, kitodoka ŋes Makanaim; 
9  Kituluo ŋes ekabaka loka Gilead, ka Iasurin, ka Yesereel, ka Epuraim, ka Benyamin, ka Isirael kere, 
10  (Kerai Is-boset okoku loka Saul loka ikar akaisaoŋon naageunia airum Isirael, kirumak ikar iarei.) Konye kotup ekek loka Yuda Daudi. 
11  Apak naaraar Daudi ekabaka koKeburon irumit ekek loka Yuda emwaasi ikar ikanykaarei ka ilapio ikanykape.


12  

Koloma Abiner okoku loka Ner, ka ibulesin luka Is-boset okoku loka Saul, anyoun koMakanaim kolot Gibeon. 
13  

Koloma Yoab okoku loka Seruia ka ikejaanakinak luka Daudi, kiriamunos kakes eiduny katapar naka Gibeon; kiboikinos, lu epuai katapar, kwi da epuai katapar. 
14  

Kotema Abiner Yoab atiar, “Keŋaiŋait, konyout ikatumunak abolia kakonyenewok.” Kotema Yoab atiar, “Aso konyoutu.” 
15  Konyout kodokasi imaritai; itomon ka luarei kanuka Benyamin, ka Is-boset okoku loka Saul, ka itomon ka luarei luka ikejaanakinak luka Daudi. 
16  Kitiŋ ŋinituŋanan akou naka aupake, kicum kekilenike osiep loka aupake; kibiroros nepepe: kanuka ŋun ŋes amaikinere aibois ŋin Kelakat-kasurim,

naejai Gibeon. 
17  

Kosisior ejie kapaaran kaŋin; kipikoroi Abiner ka ituŋa luka Isirael kakonyen nuka ikejaanakinak luka Daudi.


18  

Ajaas kanen odwe iuni luka Seruia, Yoab ka Abisai, ka Asakel: ketirono Asakel akerit kwape kamori. 
19  Korukitor Asakel Abiner; mam abu kibelokin teten arai kediany kotoma alositeke naatupitor Abiner. 
20  Kosodi Abiner anoliar kauke, kotema atiar, “Ŋes ijo, Asakel?” Koboŋok ebe, “Eoŋ ca lo.” 
21  

Kotema Abiner ŋes atiar, “Kibelokin ijo teten arai kediany, kikam ediopet kokatumunak, kolem lujiisike.” Konye koŋer Asakel aibelokin katupit ŋes. 
22  Kotema bobo Abiner Asakel ebe, “Kibelokin kinyek atupit eoŋ: kanukinyo kebirokinia jo kwap? Ekonakini ai aseseni onacekon Yoab?” 
23  

Konye koŋer aibelokin: tape Abiner icumi ŋes akoik ekaukau kakwara, kipelun akwara kokauke; kibirokin nen, kotwanik aibois ŋin: kosodi kanen, luadolunete kere aibois naebirokin Asakel kotwanite, kobwout.


24  

Konye apotu Yoab ka Abisai korukioto Abiner: koloma akoloŋ nakedolioto kesi oukot loka Ama, loitei Gia korot loka amodiŋ naka Gibeon. 
25  Kotukonokinos idwe luka Benyamin neajai Abiner, koraut erioŋet ediopet, kobwaata kokuju keukot. 
26  

Kosodi Abiner aiworo Yoab ebe, “Edanyi kereka ekileŋ ikar kere? Mam jo ijeni ebe awasiake ŋes adwaris? Aso do kitodoli ai eriŋa icorakinia ituŋa aboŋor katupakin iinacanakec?” 
27  

Kotema Yoab atiar, “Kwape ejaria Edeke, kemam jo einer, abeit tikeloto ituŋa tupuruc, komam ŋinituŋanan atupit onaceke.” 
28  Kokut Yoab arupepe, kobwoutu ituŋa kere, komam bobo erukitotor Isirael, karaida aitiji kes bobo.


29  

Kotuboros Abiner ka ituŋake Araba, koloto akuare kia; kodokasi Yorodan, kotuboros Bituron kere, kodoloto Makanaim. 
30  Koboŋo Yoab katupit Abiner: kedau atukonokin ituŋa kere, komameut ituŋa itomon ka lukanykaoŋon ka Asakel kokejaanakinak luka Daudi. 
31  Konye apotu ikejaanakinak luka Daudi kodanyata luka Benyamin, ka ituŋa luka Abiner, tape etwakete ituŋa akwat auni ka akaisakanykape. 
32  

Kodakasi Asakal, kidaikis ŋes ates naka papake, naajai Bet-lekem, Kolot Yoab ka ituŋake akuare kia, kocila kide kojaas kesi Keburon.

